<Base>
<div class="shell"><nav><div class="nwa play" id="nwa"><span class="big"><span class="ch">N</span><span class="ch d">.</span><span class="ch">W</span><span class="ch d">.</span><span class="ch">A</span><span class="ch d">.</span></span><span class="tag">nerd with attitude</span></div><button class="toggle" id="tg" aria-label="Toggle theme"><span class="knob" id="knob">☀</span></button></nav><section class="hero"><div class="kick" data-build style="--bd:60ms">Thomas Deschamps · Freelance AI &amp; product · Paris</div><h1><span data-build style="--bd:140ms">I turn <span class="q">&ldquo;cool if AI could&hellip;&rdquo;</span></span> <span data-build style="--bd:240ms">into things people use.</span> <span class="tomato" id="tom" data-build style="--bd:560ms">🍅</span></h1><p class="lead" data-build style="--bd:360ms"><b>Thomas Deschamps</b> — freelance product manager, ex-backend dev. I ship agents, MCP, and the occasional fashion brand.</p><div class="cta-row" data-build style="--bd:440ms"><a href="#contact" class="cta">Work with me</a><a href="#built" class="cta ghost">See what I&rsquo;ve built</a></div><div class="now" data-build style="--bd:520ms"><span class="dot"></span>Currently · <b>Senior PM @ Modjo</b> · building <b>Moire</b></div></section><section class="block" id="built"><div class="sec-h">Things I&rsquo;ve built</div><div class="built"><a class="lnk" data-reveal href="#"><span class="nm">Moire</span><span class="mt">live AI product</span></a><a class="lnk" data-reveal href="#"><span class="nm">Modjo Sales Agent</span><span class="mt">19 skills · open source</span></a><a class="lnk" data-reveal href="#"><span class="nm">modjo-cli</span><span class="mt">Go · MCP server</span></a><a class="lnk" data-reveal href="#"><span class="nm">Live Transcript</span><span class="mt">Twilio · Groq · 2h POC</span></a></div></section><section class="block" id="experience"><div class="sec-h">Experience</div><div class="tl"><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:0ms" href="https://www.modjo.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2025 →</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">Modjo<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Senior Product Manager</span></span><span class="out">Took Modjo Agents from preview to GA in 4 months, and shipped the public MCP.</span><span class="fact">€7M Series A · AI-native CRM</span></span></a><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:55ms" href="https://www.oplit.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2025</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">Oplit<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Head of Product</span></span><span class="out">Owned product strategy and roadmap; structured the team and the discovery-to-delivery process.</span><span class="fact">€2.6M seed · AI for factories</span></span></a><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:110ms" href="https://www.scaleway.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2022 – 25</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">Scaleway<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Product Manager</span></span><span class="out">Doubled Block Storage revenue and signed a strategic Apple Silicon contract.</span><span class="fact">iliad Group · EU sovereign cloud & AI</span></span></a><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:165ms" href="https://www.gitguardian.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2020 – 22</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">GitGuardian<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Product Manager</span></span><span class="out">Near-zero Enterprise churn; shipped the public API, audit logs, severity scoring, auto-remediation.</span><span class="fact">$106M raised · $50M Series C (2026)</span></span></a><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:220ms" href="https://www.leeto.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2019 – 20</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">Leeto<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Lead tech & product</span></span><span class="out">Rebuilt the CSE benefits platform: internal banking, employee portal, online shop.</span><span class="fact">later acquired by Up Coop</span></span></a><a class="row" data-reveal style="--d:275ms" href="https://aircall.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="yr">2016 – 18</span><span class="body"><span class="head"><span class="co">Aircall<span class="ext">↗</span></span><span class="ro">Backend dev → Technical Advisor</span></span><span class="out">Built a call-routing system handling 200k+ calls a day. The throughline: I have always read the code.</span><span class="fact">Centaur · $200M+ ARR · $1B unicorn</span></span></a></div></section></div><div class="cli-screen"><div class="ascii-win"><div class="aw-bar"><span class="aw-dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></span><span class="aw-title">nwa — terminal</span><span class="aw-egg-toggle"><button id="eggTheme">◐ theme</button><button id="eggExit">exit ⏎</button></span></div><div class="aw-scroll" id="awScroll"><div class="aw-body"><pre class="figlet"> ███╗   ██╗    ██╗    ██╗     █████╗ 
